Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Municipality of Talipao in the Province of Sulu to Municipality of Arolas Tulawie
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 692
An Act Changing the Name of the Municipality of Talipao in the Province of Sulu to Municipality of Arolas Tulawie
Section 1. The name of the Municipality of Talipao in the Province of Sulu is changed to Municipality of Arolas Tulawie.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: March 7, 1984
